title: False God
description:
Taylor Swift is bragging about her love life in this super sexy song. What is she really saying with these lyrics? And who else has tried the sexy religion angle? Lacey, Ana, Amy and Nick break this song down!
What did we miss? What else would you like from us? Let us know!
